How to install Ldapmapper ?
===========================

1 / You have or you would get the TARBALL Gzipped packet :
----------------------------------------------------------

Get by Rubyforge or Ultragreen servers :

$ cd /tmp
$ wget http://rubyforge.org/frs/download.php/252/ldapmapper-1.4.tar.gz
or 
$ wget http://www.ultragreen.net/downloads/ldapmapper-1.4.tar.gz
$ tar xvzf ldapmapper-1.4.tar.gz
$ cd ldapmapper-1.4
$ sudo bash
or 
$ su -
# ./setup.rb
 

2/ You have he gem file or get it from Rubyforge
------------------------------------------------

$ sudo bash
or 
$ su -
# gem ins ldapmapper-1.4.gem
or
# gem ins ldapmapper